OL,6,GWhen did a national news programme
OL,7,Gever have a temporary look?
OL,9,FFor the last couple of weeks the BBC
OL,10,FNews at Six and the BBC News at Ten
OL,11,Fhave been decamped to Studio D at New
OL,12,FBroadcasting House.
OL,14,FOnly the least observant of regular
OL,15,Fviewers wouldn't have spotted this.
OL,17,FThe set is much smaller, there are
OL,18,Ffewer standing links and the weather
OL,19,Fpresenter is not on the set.
