OL,3,CMain BBC News studio out of action for
OL,4,Cweeks only two years after relaunch
OL,6,FNo doubt many Pres fans are
OL,7,Fdisappointed the video wall showing
OL,8,Fall the regional presenters has gone
OL,9,Ftoo.
OL,11,FThere has been no word on when things
OL,12,Fwill get back to normal.
OL,14,FIt is not unusual for programmes to
OL,15,Fmove into other studios temporarily `
OL,16,Feither because of maintenance work or
OL,17,Fbecause new sets are being constructed.
OL,19,FBut I am struggling to think of
OL,20,Foccasions when it has been immediately
OL,21,Fobvious.
