OL,6,FI doubt if many people other than Pres
OL,7,Ffans noticed any of this at the time.
OL,9,FThe changes weren't immediately
OL,10,Fobvious and clearly every effort was
OL,11,Fmade to keep things looking as normal
OL,12,Fas possible.
OL,14,FHowever the current situation has a
OL,15,Fnoticeable ongoing impact on the Six
OL,16,Fand Ten.
OL,18,FPersonally I have no problem with a
OL,19,Fsmaller set ` it feels more intimate.
