OL,3,CMain BBC News studio out of action for
OL,4,Cweeks only two years after relaunch
OL,6,FBut I have argued before that this is
OL,7,Fnot 1970. There is nothing wrong in
OL,8,Fprinciple with using a number of
OL,9,Fdifferent styles for links. The normal
OL,10,Fset for the Six and Ten allows the
OL,11,Fpresenter to interact with graphics
OL,12,Fand can showcase powerful or striking
OL,13,Fimages.
OL,15,FFor now, at least, there are
OL,16,Flimitations on the ability to do that.
OL,18,FThere has been no notable effect on
OL,19,Fthe viewing figures nor am I aware of
OL,20,Fany audience feedback.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
