OL,3,CMain BBC News studio out of action for
OL,4,Cweeks only two years after relaunch
OL,6,FIf anything, the ratings have been
OL,7,Frelatively good recently, perhaps
OL,8,Freflecting the importance of the
OL,9,Fcoverage of the tragedy in Southport,
OL,10,Fthe rioting in parts of England and
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland and some excellent
OL,12,Fcoverage of Ukraine's advance into
OL,13,FRussian territory. Inheritance from
OL,14,Fthe Olympics will also have been a
OL,15,Ffactor.
OL,17,FBut there is a risk.
OL,19,FCould all this be unintentionally
OL,20,Fdemonstrating that core BBC News
OL,21,Fviewers don't want or need fancy links?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
