OL,3,CMain BBC News studio out of action for
OL,4,Cweeks only two years after relaunch
OL,6,FThe simple quality of the journalism `
OL,7,Fwhether in packages or live pieces `
OL,8,Fcan speak for itself.
OL,10,FThere is an argument for simplicity
OL,11,Fand the simple relationship a news
OL,12,Fpresenter can build with the audience
OL,13,Fsimply by talking directly to them.
OL,15,FBut context and analysis can be
OL,16,Fvisually dull so it is right to find
OL,17,Fthe most engaging and effective ways
OL,18,Fof doing this.
OL,20,FSimilarly a striking image on the set
OL,21,Fcan be more eyecatching than a
OL,22,Ftraditional inset.
