OL,3,CMain BBC News studio out of action for
OL,4,Cweeks only two years after relaunch
OL,6,F20 years ago ITV News went much
OL,7,Ffurther down this road with its bold
OL,8,FTheatre of News. That is now a distant
OL,9,Fmemory. ITV News now normally goes for
OL,10,Feither a simple medium close up shot
OL,11,For a medium close up with a
OL,12,Fstraightforward inset.
OL,14,FIt's just two years since the BBC
OL,15,Funveiled its bold new news studio. Who
OL,16,Fwould have expected it to be out of
OL,17,Faction for a significant length of
OL,18,Ftime so soon?
